UNET Block Graphing is used to optimize the merging process.
For a long time we have advocated for the use of advanced merging with many profiles and we evaluated many graphs to test the optimal profile to producing the best outputs in the style we want to achieve. Examples and explanations are below.

This model merges two excellent models together using FCH.

Waifu Diffusion 1.5 Beta 2 (for UltraHorizon V2)
Ultra Cmodel (on CivitAI)

Future versions will use later releases of either source model as an when they are released.
